{"tid":174471,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"最鐘意邊套鬼片？","createTime":"2017-03-26T21:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-30T07:32:07.000Z","uid":9767,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7870aabb9a4a6c6d5fba9cb80443f6e54e08d11d","tid":174471,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T21:10:59.000Z","msg":"個人最鐘意有溫子仁班底嘅鬼片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nINSIDIOUS 1 我第一次睇真係覺得好特別 堅恐怖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係我睇得最多次嘅鬼片 氣氛同嚇位拎得好準<br />\n<br />\nINSIDIOUS 2同3 雖則無咁經典 但都不過不失 第二集一開波即出鬼 由頭帶到尾 唔會拖拖拉拉 非常爽皮 第1集對我印象太深刻 呢個系列出新片我都一定睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nTHE CONJURING 1同2 都好撚正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 非常推薦 又係有新片都必睇<br />\n<br />\nMAMA 第一次睇 有一幕真係嚇撚到向後跌左落地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 恐怖得黎帶丁點感人 非常唔錯<br />\n<br />\nDRAG ME TO HELL 感覺非常新鮮 好撚核凸兼重口味 但效果出奇地正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBABADOOK 似魔鬼片多過鬼片 我覺得兩者係有少少分別 但都幾好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前排有套咩關燈之後都幾正 但唔算話太恐怖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為隻鬼都唔知算唔算係鬼 似超能力人多啲 唔夠靈異 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講下泰國 <br />\n<br />\n人稱神作嘅鬼影 老實講 我就覺得一般般 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反而 陰容院在 恐怖好多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 非常推薦<br />\n<br />\n嚇鬼呀嬸 雖然就搞笑感人成分居多 但都好推介 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中國<br />\n<br />\n屍憶 有關冥婚 氣氛拿捏得幾好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係幾好睇(尤其女主角) <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n日本 <br />\n<br />\n日本鬼片俾我感覺都好流下 好多時節奏太慢 畫蛇添足 唔係我鐘意嗰類 最有印象同最鐘意嘅鬼角色就係伽椰子 (佐佐木希套咒怨最尾出場爬地下嗰隻 好似係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )巴絲有無好片推介？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n舊鬼片雖然好多都好正 但有啲係細個睇會嚇撚到瀨屎 大個睇返又覺得碎料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋好多經典鬼片可能實在太久遠 啲化妝/嚇位已經嚇唔到人 但劇情就幾好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴絲有無真係正 真係恐怖嘅鬼片推薦？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6ddf80012f709de1b13234937ede22bf6af39c","tid":174471,"uid":17168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T21:48:42.000Z","msg":"agger溫子仁好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講死寂有佢份 <br />\n死寂 好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講人偶公仔 氣氛勁正 個結局好心寒<br />\n<br />\n日本最驚都係咒怨系列 細細個唔識死睇晒咁多套 到宜家都係覺得好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n泰國既話 見鬼10好恐怖又搞笑 同埋5條大路通陰間我覺得d故事都幾有娛樂性幾好睇！<br />\n<br />\n其實好鍾意睇鬼片 樓主講個d我都好似睇過但一時之間又諗唔起邊d正 最鍾意睇個d結局會嚇你一跳個d 姐係成套戲埋下好多伏筆 到最後一一解開 唔係一尾靠嚇"},{"pid":"e411b2c1b53cfc937b6d1cdf13af030fbfb4063a","tid":174471,"uid":9767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T23:18:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>agger溫子仁好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽講死寂有佢份 <br />\n死寂 好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講人偶公仔 氣氛勁正 個結局好心寒<br />\n<br />\n日本最驚都係咒怨系列 細細個唔識死睇晒咁多套 到宜家都係覺得好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n泰國既話 見鬼10好恐怖又搞笑 同埋5條大路通陰間我覺得d故事都幾有娛樂性幾好睇！<br />\n<br />\n其實好鍾意睇鬼片 樓主講個d我都好似睇過但一時之間又諗唔起邊d正 最鍾意睇個d結局會嚇你一跳個d 姐係成套戲埋下好多伏筆 到最後一一解開 唔係一尾靠嚇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人偶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢拍嘅恐怖片真係好多伏筆好撚正 <br />\n<br />\n咒怨最深刻係白老婦同黑少女 仲有就係佐佐木希做個集 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我發現只要套鬼電影係講日文就會恐怖左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過唔太鍾意佢斬開幾個故事咁講 轉黎轉去幾煩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見鬼十香港都有套 一開頭通靈嗰part幾正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nINSIDIOUS 1留左好多伏筆 未有2之前啲巴絲仲估主角係由細個已經被隻鬼搶左身體 雖然最後證明係錯嘅 但呢個推論真係好撚正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 電影最尾嗰幕絕對係經典 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3787f29705ac58c45afbefac6c7aa3906753d8","tid":174471,"uid":35508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T23:40:56.000Z","msg":"the shining"},{"pid":"bec4945a6eed4c9f9ba878b2036b2c7928c38657","tid":174471,"uid":74004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:06:04.000Z","msg":"個陣睇陰容院在做到開𨋢飛隻鬼入黎個到<br />\n唔知點解笑左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cbb14fb7c3f24743e26662e2097de0ce8db1f7a","tid":174471,"uid":9105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:16:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個陣睇陰容院在做到開𨋢飛隻鬼入黎個到<br />\n唔知點解笑左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係呢套當年係戲院第一套睇到要咪住隻眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1060a717ec74134c4c18adb98f775208fd47dc8c","tid":174471,"uid":74004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:20:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個陣睇陰容院在做到開𨋢飛隻鬼入黎個到<br />\n唔知點解笑左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係呢套當年係戲院第一套睇到要咪住隻眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢成套戲最恐怖個位應該係最尾<br />\n冇啦啦話睇我死既人都要死<br />\n即刻代入左好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96da6b745f69a9f124a195642f9abcfe9a1e5812","tid":174471,"uid":38790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T06:24:47.000Z","msg":"有冇睇過熱血青年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開頭聽個名以為好正路<br />\n點知原來係鬼片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fda0d351779f6ef0e890f24158b593c3a76dfed","tid":174471,"uid":8150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T07:09:13.000Z","msg":"近幾年都係<br />\nthe witch <br />\nit follows<br />\nbabadook<br />\nas above so below<br />\n<br />\n再之前既就<br />\nlet the right one in / a girl walks home alone at night (吸血鬼都當係鬼)<br />\nthe orphanage<br />\nthe devil's backbone <br />\nthe others<br />\nblair wi